+- [ ] Tests written or updated
+- [ ] Code implemented
+- [ ] API contracts updated, if needed
+- [ ] Database rules followed, if needed
+- [ ] Permissions tested
+- [ ] Audit events tested
+- [ ] Tests/typecheck/lint/build passed
+- [ ] Risk assessment completed
