+- `docs/source/screen-spec-member-portal.md` MP07, MP11, MP13, §§8.2-8.4, 10, 11, and 14.3-14.4
+- `docs/source/functional-spec.md` M03-FR-010 through M03-FR-012 and M06-FR-018-019
