- [008L4 — Portal Production Boundary and Browser Proof](/Users/amitkallapa/LMS/.ralph/worktrees/2026-07-15_181520_architecture_review/docs/slices/008L4-portal-production-boundary-and-browser-proof.md:1)

008M now depends on 008L4. Ralph state, context, progress, handoff, digests, and the architecture-review descriptor were updated. CR-007 was reconciled into `completed_slices`; the architecture-review counter was reset. No stale blocked slices existed.

